Plintissa noticed the batttle and ran to join it, Train Wreck following.
Airbomber came running up, he didn't have Ramhorn with him, but he ran to
the base to help the Maximals. Stranato jumped up.

"Whooo!" He gave his battle cry and ran out to battle.

Sineiss and Sinister decide to go help the Preds. They go to the base and
instantly get plowed over by Stranato and a well placed and well timed
Spear. Sinesis tries to fire back but Stranato hits him with a belly to
belly suplex. Sinister runs up from behind, but Stranato catches him
and...OLYMPIC SLAM! Olympic Slam on Sinister! Sinister groans in pain.
Sinesis rises up slightly, but then mumbles in dread as Airbomber, Train
Wreck, and Plintissa arive on the scene. Stronghold and Scamrock come
running over to the base. Artist comes running in.

Artist fires at the attackers.

Plintissa and Train Wreck fire at the attackers.

Airbomber fires.

Stronghold and Scamrock run head on into the battle to get them some up
close.

Stranato started to wear down Sinesis with a sleeper hold, but Sinister
breaks it up. Stranato is double teamed and badly beaten by Sinister and
Sinesis...
